 			<refentrytitle>libxslt</refentrytitle>
 			<manvolnum>3</manvolnum>
-		</citerefentry> concludes it is in an infinite loop. The default is 3000.
+		</citerefentry> concludes it is in an infinite loop. The default is 10000.
 		</para>
 	</listitem>
 		</varlistentry>
